metadata.name: Dog Squad
metadata.description:
About the Photograph:
The photographs shows training of Dog Squad of Indian Army, a daily morning routine of the canines. In the backdrop, "The 42" one of the tallest building of India makes a frame which can never be re created.  A photograph very close to my heart, "Dog Squad" has won many awards and recognitions, and have been displayed in prestigious exhibitions. 

Specifications:
Dimensions: 4841 × 3227
Physical Copy not applicable.
